data.description: Welcome to 197 Gentle Breeze!  Located in one of Floresville's most beautiful neighborhoods of South Breeze Estates. This community is gated with every home in the street being a custom built product with each property sitting on over an acre lot. This gorgeous home has over 2300 sq ft with an open floor plan with upgraded tile flooring throughout the living areas. The kitchen is equipped with custom cabinets and granite counter tops with a built in range, oven and microwave. With four bedrooms and two and a half baths, high ceilings, and upgraded lighting throughout the interior and exterior of the home. Newly installed irrigation system, storage shed and privacy fence, this home is ready for your short commute to and from the city and ready to enjoy your family in the tranquil lifestyle of the country. Come walk your new home today, so that it is ready for you tomorrow.
